rows.label: campfev11_240_150_msg0001
rows.name:
Shin.
Worried about being away from Laura?

rows.label: campfev11_240_150_msg0003
rows.name:
Perhaps...I bear some responsibility
in this matter.

rows.label: campfev11_240_150_msg0004
rows.name: No, it's not that... I just...

rows.label: campfev11_240_150_msg0005
rows.name:
Pretty unusual for you to get rattled,
Shin

rows.label: campfev11_240_150_msg0007
rows.name:
I understand your feelings, Shin.
Well, you needn't worry

rows.label: campfev11_240_150_msg0008
rows.name:
At any rate, we should probably
get ourselves over to the flagship
as soon as possible.

rows.label: campfev11_240_150_msg0009
rows.name:
And when we've finished sharing
information, we can make our way
back to Trigo.

rows.label: campfev11_240_150_msg0010
rows.name:
Sounds good. I feel like we should take
care of this pronto, for Shin's sake

rows.label: campfev11_240_150_msg0011
rows.name:
You're only saying that because you
can't stand dealing with the stuffiness.
